title: New cell subtypes classified in mouse brain

title_detail.value: New cell subtypes classified in mouse brain

summary: An international team has created a new way to classify neurons in the mouse brain. The approach is revealing new brain cell subtypes even while bringing the BRAIN Initiative closer to its goal of comprehensively mapping a whole brain.
